"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"1. Make sure to lay the basics and build up a framework of knowledge\\n2. Find a really smart person to give you an outline and say the key points. Then you can use your existing knowledge and common sense to form a general impression of what is going on in this field. This kind of introduction is easy to understand with the use of light and heavy language. If it is not convenient to take notes at that time, it is advisable to take notes afterwards, and this \\\"note\\\" is for further digestion. If you have the opportunity to find a few more people in this area, it is better to have several times to ask for advice. It is important to have a little reverence for what the other person says, but it is not advisable to hold it as a golden rule. Ultimately, you must also combine examples to contribute to your own understanding.\\n3. Start with issues and events. Problems and events are the most likely to arouse enthusiasm for thinking. Figure out a problem, figure out an event, often let you have the feeling of sweeping a blind spot of knowledge. The knowledge and terminology on which they are loaded will also be easier to remember and better understand their meaning and usefulness because of the content of the problem and the event.\\n4. At the same time, you need to add knowledge from books or the Internet to gradually broaden the relevant knowledge and grasp it accurately.\\n\\nIf you want to summarize it, you can call it the direct access method, expanding all the way to more and more. When feeling more and more ignorant, it is the best time to know more and more.\",\"timestamp\":1636367870,\"title\":\"How do you dive into a field of knowledge quickly?\"},\"digest\":\"dfn53BAhh4njgqQoLOGr-P6ku5amzWPWNg73g7EXs6s\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x896002E29FE4CDa28A3ae139b0bf7bAc26B33a8C\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"h2SqxoyfXeJIFnAioDw5VNw_C1pHD5JKdUcA-82WbFs\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"BCFRE00CUTzo4j8SkczgDHJeWwqM7ysh-MTkZOdSIp0\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"8jZv1SdRyIyK7Jqa8p9r1kpoRpwt48ggwvsKF94ftKw2WuYN9I2JHRFD1cJHWNdhctmra3zI3GnsVpfKo-3jEQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x5041646472f1ab7ff747d98f043e1db14b8954da292890a87b10b03e1bef46b623ce87323bf57e7d87ed4f983267fbe2dbeb5ca906f43b9d8769f6c9e729ead11b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"h2SqxoyfXeJIFnAioDw5VNw_C1pHD5JKdUcA-82WbFs\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"BCFRE00CUTzo4j8SkczgDHJeWwqM7ysh-MTkZOdSIp0\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"dfn53BAhh4njgqQoLOGr-P6ku5amzWPWNg73g7EXs6s\"}"